<br>
Til 10 you will never see a hit above 20. With no weapon. Period<br>
Til 20 you will never see a hit above 30 (maybe up to 33 with heavy buffs). Period. <br>
This is some kind of antitwinking. Imaging a secondlevel Paladin with a 32/38 weapon from Dragon Necropolis. He would simply destroy everything. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
Conclusion: A cheap 17/30 (Nathsar Greatsword) or 19/30 (ornate rune blade) is the ideal weapon for levels 11 to 20.<br>
<br>
Second: A good advice is to max out every meleeskill (1hsl, 2hsl, 1hbl, 2hbl and piercing in every level). You won´t regret it.<br>
<br>
Third: Never put any training point in a meleeskill. Never. They go up anyway. Maybe you will need the points later for tradeskills.<br>
<br>
