Only put a training point into new skills, ie Double Attack, etc. to jumpstart them.  (&quot;You have learned the basics of Double Attack.&quot;)<br>
At 20, when you train double attack, you'll be at skill level 20 (average) as someone said.  This will raise quickly.<br>
<br>
